LibriVox recording of The Adventures of Sammy Jay by Thornton W. Burgess.
Read in English by Rachel
Summary to come later. A really fun adventure about a blue jay (who is very annoying!) and all the other animals in the forest. - Summary by Summary by Rachel
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.
